@startuml
object Teacher
object StudentController
object TransferStudentUseCase
object StudentWriter
object EnrollmentWriter
object ClassroomReaderFunctions
object StudentDiscordMembershipService
object BalanceSnapshotReader
object Database <<database>>
Teacher --> StudentController : 1: transfer request
StudentController --> TransferStudentUseCase : 2: execute
TransferStudentUseCase --> StudentWriter : 3: require active student
StudentWriter --> Database : 4: SELECT student
TransferStudentUseCase --> ClassroomReaderFunctions : 5: ensure active class
TransferStudentUseCase --> EnrollmentWriter : 6: load active enrollment
TransferStudentUseCase --> EnrollmentWriter : 7: close old enrollment
TransferStudentUseCase --> EnrollmentWriter : 8: create new enrollment
TransferStudentUseCase --> StudentDiscordMembershipService : 9: join current class guild if possible
TransferStudentUseCase --> BalanceSnapshotReader : 10: load balance
TransferStudentUseCase --> StudentController : 11: summary
@enduml
